sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Page as Page Component
    participant Store as Zustand Store
    participant API as XiabanyaApi
    participant Toaster as sonner Toaster
    participant DOM as DOM/Animation

    Note over Page: === 页面加载流程 ===

    Page->>Store: fetchTodayRecords()
    Store->>Page: loading = true
    Page->>Page: 渲染 Skeleton 骨架屏

    Store->>API: api.records.list({start, end})
    
    alt 成功 & 有数据
        API-->>Store: ActivityRecord[]
        Store->>Page: loading = false, records = [...]
        Page->>Page: 渲染数据列表
    else 成功 & 空数据
        API-->>Store: []
        Store->>Page: loading = false, records = []
        Page->>Page: 渲染 EmptyState 组件
    else 失败
        API-->>Store: Error
        Store->>Page: loading = false, error = true
        Page->>Page: 渲染 Error EmptyState + 重试按钮
        Page->>Toaster: toast.error("加载失败")
    end

    Note over Page: === 用户操作流程 ===

    User->>Page: 点击操作按钮
    Page->>Page: 按钮进入 loading 状态
    Page->>API: api.tracker.start()
    
    alt 成功
        API-->>Page: void
        Page->>Page: 按钮恢复 + 状态更新
        Page->>Toaster: toast.success("操作成功")
        Toaster-->>User: 绿色 Toast 滑入
    else 失败
        API-->>Page: Error
        Page->>Page: 按钮恢复
        Page->>Toaster: toast.error("操作失败")
        Toaster-->>User: 红色 Toast 滑入
    end

    Note over Toaster: === Toast 生命周期 ===

    Page->>Toaster: toast.success("操作成功")
    Toaster->>Toaster: 生成唯一 id
    Toaster->>DOM: 创建 toast 节点
    DOM->>DOM: slide-in 动画 (250ms)
    Note over DOM: 显示 3000ms (success)
    DOM->>DOM: slide-out 动画 (200ms)
    DOM->>Toaster: 移除节点

    Note over Page: === 报告生成流程 ===
    Page->>Toaster: toast.loading("正在生成报告...")
    Page->>API: api.reports.generate(params)
    API-->>Page: Report { content }
    Page->>Toaster: toast.dismiss() + toast.success("报告已生成")
    Page->>Page: 渲染 Markdown 预览
